 {"id":"frankenredis-xy1q","title":"[HIGH] XADD auto-ID + broad stream divergences — fixture clock vs upstream wall clock","description":"Surfaced by live_redis_core_stream_matches_runtime: 48/218 divergences; the majority stem from XADD auto-generated IDs using the fixture now_ms (e.g. '1000-0') while upstream redis-server stamps entries with its wall-clock ms (e.g. '1777004357777-0'). Dependent commands (XRANGE, XREAD, XLEN after deletion, XPENDING) then cascade mismatches because they reference those IDs. Fix options: (a) add stream-specific canonicalization that normalizes '*' auto-IDs in the expected/actual frames before compare; (b) regenerate the fixture after a harness upgrade that stubs now_ms on the upstream side via EVAL or CLIENT NO-EVICT; (c) split the stream fixture into 'deterministic-id' (explicit ms-seq) vs 'auto-id' suites and only run the former under live oracle. Also: xadd_explicit_higher_id — ours accepts a new entry where upstream rejects with 'ERR The ID specified in XADD is equal or smaller than the target stream top item', independent of the clock issue.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-24T04:21:15.953055702Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-24T04:21:15.953055702Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"frankenredis-b2qs","title":"[HIGH] PFMERGE TTL verify off-by-2ms (live oracle harness clock drift)","description":"Surfaced by live_redis_core_hyperloglog_matches_runtime: single divergence pfmerge_ttl_verify_ttl_after expects Integer(59998) vs our Integer(60000). Upstream's TTL has decremented by the ~2ms of wall-clock elapsed between PFMERGE and the verification PTTL; our fixture clock doesn't advance. Likely a fixture-clock-vs-wall-clock issue, not a functional bug. Fix: either (a) loosen the expected PTTL to a range [59990, 60000] in the fixture, or (b) add a PTTL tolerance in the differential comparator for time-advance cases.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-24T04:22:31.040076973Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-24T04:22:31.040076973Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
